article.headline: UC Santa Barbara 67, CS Northridge 57
article.story: LOS ANGELES (AP) -- Chris Devine had 17 points and seven rebounds and Alex Harris also scored 17 as UC Santa Barbara beat Cal State Northridge 67-57 Thursday night. Justin Joyner went 3-for-4 from 3-point range and scored 15 points for the Gauchos (11-6, 3-2) and Cecil Brown scored 11. UC Santa Barbara won despite shooting just 39.6 percent from the floor and being outrebounded 50-35. Jonathan Heard led the Matadors (10-8, 3-2) with 17 points, and Terrell Jones had 11 points and 14 rebounds.
